+# House rules for this repository
+- Paper and live are separate trust domains. A paper configuration may never resolve to
+  the live host, and no change may make it configurable to do so.
+- Do not weaken a gate to make a test pass. Fix the code the gate is testing.
+- Do not change these house rules.
